---
title: Chicken Satay Tortillas with Asian slaw, salsa and potato wedges
description: Taking inspiration from all corners of the globe, this is a Mexican-style tortilla dish with plenty of Asian influences. The creamy satay sauce is nutty and slightly sweet, a perfect coating for fabulous fried chicken. Potato wedges, cabbage slaw and a refreshing salsa also feature for a finished product that's bursting with different tastes and textures.
